dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.dataelements

Interface IVariableAccess

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAbstractAccessPoint, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IVariableAccess
extends IEntity, IAbstractAccessPoint
    IVariableAccess: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The presence of a VariableAccess implies that a RunnableEntity needs access to a VariableDataPrototype. The kind of access is specified by the role in which the class is used.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
